{"tha-ap455:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap455:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap455:0.3":"3 Sihasanabijiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap455:1.1":"“Tissassaham bhagavato, ","tha-ap455:1.2":"bodhirukkhamavandiyam; ","tha-ap455:1.3":"Paggayha bijanim tattha, ","tha-ap455:1.4":"sihasanamabijaham. ","tha-ap455:2.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap455:2.2":"sihasanamabijaham; ","tha-ap455:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap455:2.4":"bijanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap455:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap455:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap455:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap455:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap455:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap455:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap455:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap455:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap455:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap455:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sihasanabijiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap455:7.1":"Sihasanabijiyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}